76. Write a simple &#39;birthday countdown&#39; script, the script will count the number of days between
current day and birthday.

&lt;?php
$birthday = &quot;2025-12-31&quot;;
$currentDate = date(&quot;Y-m-d&quot;);

$diff = strtotime($birthday) - strtotime($currentDate);
$daysLeft = floor($diff / (60 * 60 * 24));

echo &quot;Days left until birthday: &quot; . $daysLeft;
?&gt;
output:

Days left until birthday: 365
